Changing password by token in OKTA platform. Please check below files:
- password_changer:  a web_api password changer.
- template_token:    a secret with okta token is created basing on the template
- template_user:     a secret with username/password is created basing on the template.  The secret can be used to launch web_browsing to connect OKTA, and do password changer with associated secret.
- secret_config_example:  It is an example to configure target and secrets basing  template_user/template_token and password_changer.
